   --/  * sfKeyF13:      The F13 key
   --/  * sfKeyF14:      The F14 key
   --/  * sfKeyF15:      The F15 key
   --/  * sfKeyPause:    The Pause key
   --/  * sfKeyCount:    Keep last -- the total number of keyboard keys
